rivers-licence-new-drivers#section-2">Apply for a driver=E2=80=99s licence<=
/a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.ontario.ca/page/get-g-drivers-licence-ne=
w-drivers#section-3">Where to apply</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.onta=
rio.ca/page/get-g-drivers-licence-new-drivers#section-4">Accepted identity =
documents</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.ontario.ca/page/get-g-drivers-=
licence-new-drivers#section-5">Fees</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.onta=
rio.ca/page/get-g-drivers-licence-new-drivers#section-6">Study for the know=
ledge test</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.ontario.ca/page/get-g-drivers=
-licence-new-drivers#section-7">Learning to drive: graduated licensing</a><=
/li><li><a href=3D"https://www.ontario.ca/page/get-g-drivers-licence-new-dr=
ivers#section-8">Booking a road test</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.ont=
ario.ca/page/get-g-drivers-licence-new-drivers#section-9">Videos</a></li><l=
i class=3D"related-li"><a href=3D"https://www.ontario.ca/page/get-g-drivers=
-licence-new-drivers#section-related">Related</a></li></ol>

